        {
            "title": "諾比侃與浪潮智慧城市訂戰略合作框架 料合作總規模約5億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">諾比侃(02635)發自願公告，披露與國內智慧城市企業浪潮智慧城市訂立戰略合作框架協議，預計合作規模約5億元(人民幣．下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"諾比侃官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/Nuobikan-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"諾比侃官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/Nuobikan-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">諾比侃官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">依照戰略合作協議，雙方將圍繞智慧城市、城市安全、城市治理、城市數字基礎設施等核心領域開展AI智能化深度合作。雙方已就合作機制、核心方向達成高度共識，正組建專屬對接與研發團隊，建立項目推進機制等工作，並將引入優質第三方合作夥伴，打造多方協同產業體系，共建全國性智能化標桿項目。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公告又指，浪潮智慧城市擁有全國70餘個城市的智慧城市建設運營經驗、成熟市場布局及資<br/>  源整合優勢。通過戰略合作，雙方將在技術、場景及全國市場等核心方面產生協同優勢。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898599-%e8%ab%be%e6%af%94%e4%be%83%e8%88%87%e6%b5%aa%e6%bd%ae%e6%99%ba%e6%85%a7%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82%e8%a8%82%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c%e6%a1%86%e6%9e%b6-%e6%96%99%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c%e7%b8%bd%e8%a6%8f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/02635.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 08:44:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "和譽折讓8.35%配股籌5.23億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">和譽(02256)今早公布，擬配售4290萬股集資約5.23億元；配股價12.18元，較該股昨收市價13.29元折讓8.35%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：和譽官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260421_FI_source-web_02256.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：和譽官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260421_FI_source-web_02256.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：和譽官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股前5個交易日平均收市價13.43元計，配股價較之折讓約9.31%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資所得淨額約5.17億元，當中約90%用作研發創新的腫瘤及非腫瘤候選藥物、推進國際多中心臨床試驗及潛在的商業化活動；約10%用作一般及公司用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898587-%e5%92%8c%e8%ad%bd%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%938-35%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c5-23%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/02256.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 08:40:16",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "寧德時代小股東減持5800萬A股初步定價每股410.34人幣 涉款238億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(03750)昨晚公布，小股東寧波聯合創新擬減持5800萬股寧德時代A股(300750.SZ)一事，詢價得出初步轉讓價每股410.34元(人民幣．下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代溧陽基地.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代溧陽基地.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以上述轉讓價計算，寧波聯合創新減持套現近238億元；交易完成後，持股將由6.23%降至4.96%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公告指出，今次詢價轉讓不通過集中競價交易方式或大宗交易方式進行，不屬於通過二級市場減持。參與詢價轉讓報價及申購的機構投資者共50名，涵蓋基金管理公司、合格境外機構投資者、保險公司、證券翁石、私募基金管理人、信託公司等專業機構投資者，有效認購數量1.21億股，認購倍數2.1倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">初步確定獲配股份的受讓方共30名，涉及股份在受讓後6個月內不得轉讓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">受讓方</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898572-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e5%b0%8f%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%b8%9b%e6%8c%815800%e8%90%aca%e8%82%a1%e5%88%9d%e6%ad%a5%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a1410-34%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3-%e6%b6%89",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_CATL.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 08:29:53",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期高水逾120點 重磅港股ADR多半遍好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時12分升142點或0.54%，報26485點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報26449點，較香港上日現貨收市高88點或0.33%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣523.1元，較上日香港收市高0.62元或0.12%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣137.2元，較上日香港收市高0.19元或0.14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣85.5元，較上日香港收市高0.31元或0.37%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣122.8元，較上日香港收市高0.41元或0.34%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣32.5元，較上日香港收市高0.14元或0.44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣143.4元，較上日香港收市高1.23元或0.86%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣84.2元，較上日香港收市高0.69元或0.83%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣413.7元，較上日香港收市高2.14元或0.52%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣61.9元，較上日香港收市高0.4元或0.64%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.9元，較上日香港收市低0.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報26494點，升104點，較上日恒指收市26361點，高水133點。科指期貨夜市收報5092點，較上日科指收市高水26點；國指期貨夜市收報8941點，較上日國指收市高水42點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898564-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be120%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%a4%9a%e5%8d%8a%e9%81%8d%e5%a5%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 08:19:50",
